* Support normal modern web browsers e.g. Chrome, Firefox, Safari
* Support iOS
* Support loading .jpg and .gif images (define HAVE_JPEG and HAVE_GIF when building):
  http://anongit.freedesktop.org/git/libjpeg.git/
* Remove jsg.load, instead use AMD or CJS library loading mechanism:
  http://requirejs.org/docs/whyamd.html
